message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product to you. This exceptional item has been meticulously crafted and tailored to meet your specific needs, valued at $12000 to you. I am offering this remarkable product to you at an exclusive price of $14000. I believe this offer provides a unique opportunity for you to benefit from its high-quality features while also securing a favorable deal. Please let me know if you would like to proceed with this offer.
